 <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-81-7017-332-8\" title=\"Special:BookSources/978-81-7017-332-8\">978-81-7017-332-8</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Music+Of+India&amp;rft.pages=41-42&amp;rft.pub=Abhinav+Publications&amp;rft.date=1996&amp;rft.isbn=978-81-7017-332-8&amp;rft.au=Reginald+Massey&amp;rft.au=Jamila+Massey&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DyySNDP9XVggC%26pg%3DPA41&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ASarangadeva\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Ramanlal Chhotalal Mehta, <i>Musical Musings: Selected Essays</i>, Indian Musicological Society (1996), p. 46</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation book\">T. V. Kuppuswami (1992). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://books.google.com/books?id=LpLmAAAAMAAJ\"><i>Carn\u0101tic Music and the Tamils</i></a>. Kalinga Publications. pp.&#160;vii\u2013viii. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-81-85163-25-3\" title=\"Special:BookSources/978-81-85163-25-3\">978-81-85163-25-3</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Carn%C4%81tic+Music+and+the+Tamils&amp;rft.pages=vii-viii&amp;rft.pub=Kalinga+Publications&amp;rft.date=1992&amp;rft.isbn=978-81-85163-25-3&amp;rft.au=T.+V.+Kuppuswami&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DLpLmAAAAMAAJ&am